&nbsp;
The box and the giant screen of the stage were about to crush the candidate > and his collaborators who saved themselves for a breath. But the structure collapsed on the public in the first rows. Shortly after, in a video in which he appeared completely dressed in black, the governor of Nuevo Leon, Samuel Garcia, asked the population to repair themselves in their homes from the storm: "Fifteen minutes ago, there was a disgrace. The strong wind knocked down a stage, unfortunately there are wounded. Security forces and ambulances are already there." Later, in press statements, Garcia confirmed that there were nine dead and at least 121 wounded. >
